<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>مافيا - لعبة الكوتشينة</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg-dark: #0f0f1a;
    --bg-card: #1a1a2e;
    --bg-card-hover: #252542;
    --primary: #e94560;
    --primary-dark: #c13651;
    --accent: #ffd700;
    --accent-dark: #c5a000;
    --success: #00d9a3;
    --danger: #ff4757;
    --warning: #ffa502;
    --info: #3498db;
    --text: #f1f1f1;
    --text-muted: #a0a0b0;
    --border: #2a2a45;
    --shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    --radius: 16px;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark) 0%, #16162a 100%);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }

  /* Animations */
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.05); } }
  @keyframes glow { 0%,100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(233,69,96,0.3); } 50% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(233,69,96,0.6); } }
  @keyframes slideIn { from { transform: translateX(100%); opacity: 0; } to { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 1; } }
  @keyframes float { 0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(-10px); } }
  @keyframes nightPulse { 0%,100% { box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(52,152,219,0.2); } 50% { box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(52,152,219,0.5); } }
  @keyframes deathShake { 0%,100% { transform: translateX(0); } 20% { transform: translateX(-10px); } 40% { transform: translateX(10px); } 60% { transform: translateX(-5px); } 80% { transform: translateX(5px); } }

  .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease forwards; }
  .slide-in { animation: slideIn 0.4s ease forwards; }

  /* Header */
  .game-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .game-header h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(233,69,96,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .game-header p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .logo-icon { font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 10px; animation: float 3s ease infinite; }

  /* Screens */
  .screen { display: none; }
  .screen.active { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease; }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 14px 32px; border: none; border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease; text-decoration: none; color: white;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .btn-primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark)); }
  .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(233,69,96,0.4); }
  .btn-accent { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-dark)); color: #1a1a2e; }
  .btn-accent:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(255,215,0,0.3); }
  .btn-success { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--success), #00b894); }
  .btn-danger { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--danger), #e84118); }
  .btn-info { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--info), #2980b9); }
  .btn-dark { background: var(--bg-card); border: 2px solid var(--border); }
  .btn-dark:hover { background: var(--bg-card-hover); border-color: var(--primary); }
  .btn-sm { padding: 8px 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .btn-lg { padding: 18px 48px; font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .btn:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none !important; }

  .btn-group { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin-top: 20px; }

  /* Cards */
  .card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .card:hover { border-color: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .card-title { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--accent); }

  /* Forms */
  .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .form-label { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .form-input, .form-select, .form-textarea {
    width: 100%; padding: 14px 18px; border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px; background: var(--bg-dark); color: var(--text);
    font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .form-input:focus, .form-select:focus, .form-textarea:focus {
    outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(233,69,96,0.1);
  }
  .form-textarea { min-height: 100px; resize: vertical; }

  /* Player List */
  .players-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .player-item {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .player-item:hover { border-color: var(--primary); }
  .player-item.dead { opacity: 0.5; border-color: var(--danger); }
  .player-item.dead::after {
    content: '☠️'; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%); font-size: 3rem; opacity: 0.3;
  }
  .player-item.muted { border-color: var(--warning); }
  .player-avatar {
    width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.2rem; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .player-info { flex: 1; }
  .player-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .player-role { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .player-status { font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 600; }
  .status-alive { background: rgba(0,217,163,0.2); color: var(--success); }
  .status-dead { background: rgba(255,71,87,0.2); color: var(--danger); }
  .status-muted { background: rgba(255,165,2,0.2); color: var(--warning); }

  /* Role Cards */
  .role-card {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .role-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--primary); }
  .role-card.selected { border-color: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,215,0,0.2); }
  .role-card .role-icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .role-card .role-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .role-card .role-desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }
  .role-card .role-count {
    position: absolute; top: 10px; left: 10px;
    background: var(--primary); color: white;
    width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  /* Playing Cards */
  .playing-card {
    width: 140px; height: 200px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #f0f0f0 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    border: 3px solid #ddd;
  }
  .playing-card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(2deg); }
  .playing-card.red { border-color: var(--danger); color: var(--danger); }
  .playing-card.black { border-color: #333; color: #333; }
  .playing-card .card-suit { font-size: 3rem; }
  .playing-card .card-value { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 900; }
  .playing-card .card-role { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 8px; text-align: center; padding: 0 8px; color: #555; }
  .card-back {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark));
    border-color: var(--primary-dark);
  }
  .card-back .card-pattern {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 10px, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 10px, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 20px);
    border-radius: 13px;
  }

  /* Night Phase */
  .night-overlay {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: rgba(5,5,15,0.95);
    z-index: 1000;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
  }
  .night-title {
    font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--info);
    text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(52,152,219,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 20px; animation: pulse 2s ease infinite;
  }
  .night-subtitle { font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .night-icon { font-size: 5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; animation: float 3s ease infinite; }

  /* Phase Steps */
  .phase-steps {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; margin: 30px 0; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .phase-step {
    padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 30px;
    background: var(--bg-dark); border: 2px solid var(--border);
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .phase-step.active { border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(255,215,0,0.1); color: var(--accent); }
  .phase-step.done { border-color: var(--success); background: rgba(0,217,163,0.1); color: var(--success); opacity: 0.7; }

  /* Action Panel */
  .action-panel {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 30px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .action-title { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .action-desc { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .action-targets { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 20px 0; }
  .target-btn {
    padding: 12px 24px; border: 2px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--bg-card); color: var(--text); font-family: inherit;
    font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .target-btn:hover { border-color: var(--primary); background: var(--bg-card-hover); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .target-btn.selected { border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(255,215,0,0.1); color: var(--accent); }
  .target-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.3; cursor: not-allowed; }

  /* Dashboard */
  .dashboard-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .dashboard-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .dashboard-panel {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .panel-header {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .panel-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--accent); }
  .panel-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; }

  .event-log {
    max-height: 300px; overflow-y: auto;
    background: var(--bg-dark); border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .event-item { padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .event-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .event-time { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; margin-left: 8px; }
  .event-kill { color: var(--danger); }
  .event-save { color: var(--success); }
  .event-mute { color: var(--warning); }
  .event-reveal { color: var(--info); }

  /* Day Results */
  .day-results {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,215,0,0.1), rgba(233,69,96,0.1));
    border: 2px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 30px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }
  .day-results h2 { font-size: 2rem; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .result-item {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px; padding: 12px; margin: 8px 0;
    background: var(--bg-dark); border-radius: 12px;
  }

  /* Voting */
  .voting-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin: 20px 0; }
  .vote-card {
    background: var(--bg-dark); border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .vote-card:hover { border-color: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .vote-card.voted { border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(255,215,0,0.1); }
  .vote-count { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent); margin-top: 8px; }

  /* Winner Modal */
  .modal-overlay {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); z-index: 2000;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
  }
  .modal-content {
    background: var(--bg-card); border: 2px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 40px; max-width: 500px; width: 90%;
    text-align: center; animation: pulse 2s ease infinite;
  }
  .modal-title { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .mafia-win { color: var(--danger); }
  .citizens-win { color: var(--success); }

  /* Toggle Switch */
  .toggle-group { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin: 12px 0; }
  .toggle-switch {
    position: relative; width: 56px; height: 28px;
    background: var(--border); border-radius: 28px; cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .toggle-switch.active { background: var(--success); }
  .toggle-switch::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 2px; right: 2px;
    width: 24px; height: 24px; background: white; border-radius: 50%;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .toggle-switch.active::after { right: 30px; }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .game-header h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .playing-card { width: 100px; height: 150px; }
    .dashboard-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .btn { padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  }

  /* Scrollbar */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg-dark); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); border-radius: 4px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--primary); }

  /* Stats Bar */
  .stats-bar {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 30px;
    background: var(--bg-card); padding: 16px;
    border-radius: var(--radius); margin-bottom: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .stat-item { text-align: center; }
  .stat-value { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .stat-mafia { color: var(--danger); }
  .stat-citizen { color: var(--success); }
  .stat-total { color: var(--info); }

  /* Reveal Card */
  .reveal-card {
    position: fixed; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    z-index: 1500; background: var(--bg-card); border: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 24px; padding: 40px; text-align: center; min-width: 300px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(255,215,0,0.3); animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
  }
  .reveal-role-icon { font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .reveal-role-name { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .reveal-player-name { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text); }

  /* Tooltip */
  .tooltip {
    position: relative; cursor: help;
  }
  .tooltip::after {
    content: attr(data-tip); position: absolute; bottom: 120%; right: 50%; transform: translateX(50%);
    background: var(--bg-dark); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem; white-space: nowrap; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .tooltip:hover::after { opacity: 1; bottom: 130%; }
</style>
<base target="_blank">
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="game-header">
    <div class="logo-icon">🎴</div>
    <h1>لعبة المافيا</h1>
    <p>نظام الكوتشينة المتكامل - إدارة الأدمن</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Screen 1: Main Menu -->
  <div id="screen-menu" class="screen active">
    <div class="card" style="text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <div class="card-title" style="font-size: 1.8rem;">🎮 مرحباً بك في لعبة المافيا</div>
      <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.8;">
        لعبة استراتيجية تعتمد على الكوتشينة (ورق اللعب) لتوزيع الأدوار.<br>
        الأدمن هو المسؤول عن إدارة اللعبة وسرد الأحداث، ولا يشارك كلاعب.
      </p>
      <div style="display: grid; gap: 16px; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" onclick="showScreen('screen-setup')">
          🚀 إنشاء غرفة جديدة (أدمن)
        </button>
        <button class="btn btn-dark btn-lg" onclick="showScreen('screen-join')">
          👁️ دخول كمشاهد/لاعب
        </button>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background: var(--bg-dark); border-radius: 12px;">
        <div style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 12px;">📋 الأدوار المتاحة:</div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; justify-content: center;">
          <span style="background: rgba(255,71,87,0.2); color: var(--danger); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">🃏 الآس الأحمر - مافيا القتل</span>
          <span style="background: rgba(50,50,50,0.5); color: #aaa; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">🃏 الآس الأسود - مافيا التسكيت</span>
          <span style="background: rgba(0,217,163,0.2); color: var(--success); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">👦 الولد - الصالح المنتقم</span>
          <span style="background: rgba(52,152,219,0.2); color: var(--info); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">👴 الشايب - الطبيب</span>
          <span style="background: rgba(155,89,182,0.2); color: #bb8fce; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">👧 البنت السنك - المحقق</span>
          <span style="background: rgba(255,215,0,0.2); color: var(--accent); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">🤡 الجوكر - القناص</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Screen 2: Setup -->
  <div id="screen-setup" class="screen">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">⚙️ إعدادات الغرفة</div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="form-label">👤 اسم الأدمن (لا يلعب)</label>
        <input type="text" id="admin-name" class="form-input" placeholder="أدخل اسمك كمسؤول">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="form-label">🎯 شروط فوز المافيا</label>
        <div style="background: var(--bg-dark); padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid var(--border);">
          <div class="toggle-group" onclick="toggleWinCondition(1)" style="cursor: pointer;">
            <div id="win-toggle-1" class="toggle-switch active"></div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-weight: 700;">الخيار الأول (الأساسي)</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);">تفوز المافيا إذا تساوى عدد المافيا (الإجمالي) مع عدد الصالحين الأحياء</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="toggle-group" onclick="toggleWinCondition(2)" style="cursor: pointer; margin-top: 12px;">
            <div id="win-toggle-2" class="toggle-switch"></div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-weight: 700;">الخيار الثاني (الاحتياطي)</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);">تفوز المافيا إذا تساوى عدد المافيا (الأحياء فقط) مع عدد المواطنين الأحياء</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="form-label">👥 إضافة اللاعبين</label>
